OL,6,FDorothy 'Dot' Miles became deaf after
OL,7,Fcatching meningitis as a child.
OL,9,FShe attended the Manchester School for
OL,10,FDeaf children. In her 20s, she won a
OL,11,Fscholarship to Gallaudet University in
OL,12,FWashington DC, one of the leading
OL,13,Funiversities for the education of deaf
OL,14,Fand hard-of-hearing people.
OL,16,FShe went on to have a career in the
OL,17,Farts, performing with the US National
OL,18,FTheatre for the Deaf.
